name: WILL POWER
bio: WILL POWER: Comics Lindsay Adams and Ever Mainard Host WILLPOWER. Will power gives life advice to audience members and give "spiritual" ted-like talks.   Comics are urged to tell true stories of where they don't feel good enough and Lindsay and Ever yell positive affirmations to them.  Lindsay and Ever act as spiritual life guides and interpret the comics set and give them satirical new-age advice.
